# Integer-First Lifecycle Fields

- Prefer integers (constants or int-backed enums) over free-form strings for statuses and modes.
- For new stateful columns, define stable numeric constants in code and keep mappings centralized.
- Avoid comparing magic string literals in queries and conditionals.
- When migrating existing string states, add a backfill path and keep compatibility during rollout.
- Ensure UI labels remain translation-driven; numbers are persistence, not presentation.
